TITLE: Retrieve Private Connection String
DESCRIPTION: This output retrieves the private connection string of the MongoDB Atlas cluster with Network Peering and Custom DNS enabled. This is useful for connections within a private network using peered VPCs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mongodb/terraform-provider-mongodbatlas/blob/master/docs/resources/cluster.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
output "private" {
    value = mongodbatlas_cluster.cluster-test.connection_strings[0].private
}
```

