TITLE: Create Stream Processor (Cluster to Kafka) - Terraform
DESCRIPTION: Defines a Stream Processor that transfers data from a Cluster connection to a Kafka connection. The pipeline configuration specifies the source and emit connections, along with the target Kafka topic. The processor is initialized in the 'CREATED' state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mongodb/terraform-provider-mongodbatlas/blob/master/docs/data-sources/stream_processor.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: Terraform
