TITLE: Retrieve Sharded Cluster Information - Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to retrieve information about a sharded MongoDB Atlas cluster using the `mongodbatlas_advanced_clusters` data source. This specific example uses `use_replication_spec_per_shard = true` to manage asymmetric shards, meaning shards with different configurations.
