TITLE: Cloud Backup Snapshot Export Job Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This Terraform configuration demonstrates how to create a snapshot export bucket, initiate a snapshot export job with custom data, and then retrieve the export job details using the `mongodbatlas_cloud_backup_snapshot_export_job` data source. It requires a project ID, cluster name, and snapshot ID, as well as an export bucket ID.
