TITLE: Ignore Changes with Lifecycle Customization - Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This Terraform configuration demonstrates how to use lifecycle ignore customizations to prevent unintended changes when enabling auto-scaling in MongoDB Atlas. By ignoring changes to `disk_size_gb`, `instance_size`, and `disk_iops` attributes, Terraform will not revert automatically scaled values back to the original configuration.
