TITLE: Retrieving Data Lake Pipeline Runs using Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This Terraform configuration shows how to define a `mongodbatlas_data_lake_pipeline_runs` data source to retrieve Data Lake Pipeline Runs, given a `project_id` and `pipeline_name`. It assumes that a project and cluster have already been set up in other blocks, as well as a data lake pipeline.
