TITLE: Create Kafka Stream Connection - Terraform
DESCRIPTION: Configures a connection to a Kafka cluster using the `mongodbatlas_stream_connection` resource. It includes details like authentication mechanism, username, password, bootstrap servers, configuration properties, and security protocol.
