SOURCE: https://github.com/mongodb/terraform-provider-mongodbatlas/blob/master/examples/mongodbatlas_advanced_cluster (preview provider 2.0.0)/auto-scaling-per-shard/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: Terraform
CODE:
```
public_key           = "<MONGODB_ATLAS_PUBLIC_KEY>"
private_key          = "<MONGODB_ATLAS_PRIVATE_KEY>"
atlas_org_id         = "<MONGODB_ATLAS_ORG_ID>"
```

