TITLE: Create MongoDB Atlas Search Deployment Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This resource creates a MongoDB Atlas search deployment within a specified project and cluster. The `project_id` and `cluster_name` attributes link the deployment to an existing project and cluster.  The `specs` block defines the instance size and node count for the search nodes.
