TITLE: Retrieving Standard SRV Connection String in Terraform
DESCRIPTION: This Terraform code snippet retrieves the standard SRV connection string of an advanced MongoDB Atlas cluster.  It utilizes the `mongodbatlas_advanced_cluster` resource and accesses the `connection_strings.standard_srv` attribute. The output will be in the format `mongodb+srv://cluster-atlas.ygo1m.mongodb.net`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mongodb/terraform-provider-mongodbatlas/blob/master/docs/resources/advanced_cluster (preview provider 2.0.0).md#_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
output "standard_srv" {
    value = mongodbatlas_advanced_cluster.cluster.connection_strings.standard_srv
}
```

