TITLE: Encryption at Rest - New Usage
DESCRIPTION: This shows the new usage of `aws_kms_config`, `azure_key_vault_config`, and `google_cloud_kms_config` in the `mongodbatlas_encryption_at_rest` resource, which replace the deprecated blocks in v1.0.0. These are now using TypeSet or TypeList with MaxItems = 1.
