DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `mongodbatlas_federated_settings_org_role_mapping` resource and data source. The resource creates a federated settings organization role mapping, and the data source retrieves the created role mapping using its ID. It requires `federation_settings_id` and `org_id`.
